discourse_list.title: Know Your MIP #19 | MIP95: Cogent Bank

content.content: Know Your MIP #19 | MIP95: Cogent Bank  image1070×602 21.5 KB  For the Know Your MIP series’ 19th session, we will be walking through MIP95: $100M of Cogent Bank Loan Participations . This is a proposal by @maxglass for creating a new bespoke vault implementation for Cogent Bank, based on implantation for Huntingdon Valley Bank proposal. This MIP will be entering the February voting cycle, so be sure to check this call out before voting opens on the 13th! Sharpen your minds and bring your comments and questions!    If you can’t make to the call, post any questions you may have and we will make sure to address them during the Q&A period!  Join us! @prose11 will host   Agenda:   MIP95 presentation by Cogent Bank Q&A session   When Time in your local-timezone format: 2023-02-08T17:15:00Z Mark it on your Google Calendar!
